### Fetch Top 5 ending soon
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-ending
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json

### Fetch Top 5 by bids (default: uses stored `products.bid_count`)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-bids
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json

### Fetch Top 5 by price
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-price
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json

### CURL equivalents (for terminal)
# curl -H "apiKey: 12345ABCDE" http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-ending
# curl -H "apiKey: 12345ABCDE" http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-bids
# curl -H "apiKey: 12345ABCDE" http://localhost:3000/api/products/top-price

### List products by category (page/limit)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?catid=1&page=1&limit=20
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json

### Featch product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/detail/1
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json

### fetch related products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/related/31
apiKey: 12345ABCDE
Accept: application/json